<signature>
Perspective(float,float,float,float)
</signature>
Creates a perspective projection matrix.
/fov/ is the vertical field-of-view in degrees of the perspective matrix, /aspect/ is the aspect ratio (width divided by height).
/zNear/ and /zFar/ set up the depth clipping planes.

SA: GL::ref::LoadPixelMatrix, GL::ref::LoadProjectionMatrix, GUI::ref::matrix.